dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.systemtemplate.transformer

Interface IImplementationDataTypeElementInSystemRef

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDataPrototypeInSystemRef, IEntity

    public interface IImplementationDataTypeElementInSystemRef
extends IEntity, IDataPrototypeInSystemRef
    IImplementationDataTypeElementInSystemRef: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This meta-class represents the ability to refer to the internal structure of an AutosarDataPrototype which is typed by an ImplementationDatatype in the context of a CompositionSwComponentType. In other words, this meta-class shall not be used to model a reference to the AutosarDataPrototype as a target itself, even if the AutosarDataPrototype is typed by an ImplementationDataType and even if that ImplementationDataType represents a composite data type.
